{"tid":313082,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]三上悠亞爆料:麻友係雞係公廁","createTime":"2017-07-08T04:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T09:50:39.000Z","uid":14965,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9da1ca84082e234b4cc44b1aaaa7df1e61e336b","tid":313082,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"三上悠亞在接受採訪的時候大爆料，說自己當初入團SKE48的時候已經不是處女，而且團員有一半也不是處女。據《日刊cyzo》報導，前「AKB48」麻友加入拍攝藝人AV的片商MUTEKI，7月推出首部作品後，再接再厲第二作8月就要發售。這樣算起來，AKB48相關團體的中西里菜、城田理加、逢坂春菜、三上悠亜、川瀬友香、橘梨紗都進軍AV界，其中三上悠亞算是最有成就，在5月的DMM成人廣播獎裡面，還拿到的最優秀女優賞。<br />\n<br />\n對於這種現象，有AV作家表示，「看到三上悠亞的成功，應該會有更多的國民偶像團體進軍AV界，因為從團體畢業的人，很多都不再繼續活動，僅有少數的會繼續辦活動與粉絲交流，或是成為YouTuber，其實這樣就跟素人差不多了。最近的松田美子，就是畢業後開始出寫真DVD，但是沒有太大起色，於是在經過勸說後進軍AV界」。而身為進軍AV界的成功者，三上悠亞上個月也上《水道橋博士のムラっとびんびんテレビ》節目受訪，而且也爆很多料，像是她被AV男優清水健問說，加入的時候是處女嗎，她就說「已經不是處女了」，而且全部團體的處女跟非處女「大概一半一半」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170707/640_c23362563396886e0520851fcf827aca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170707%2F640_c23362563396886e0520851fcf827aca.jpg&h=20cc9f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMayuyu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946517f9701e217963381ce9df5bb8622ca65d76","tid":313082,"uid":8379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d2cfdcfd1537e531a1f0808ab0d2b8584cfd69","tid":313082,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:59:54.000Z","msg":"我 立即 𨳒你老母啊臭雞<br />\n架純每個毛孔都係c6精液"},{"pid":"98b799973553c626985e2c64c47099da4463dd08","tid":313082,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我 立即 𨳒你老母啊臭雞<br />\n架純每個毛孔都係c6精液</blockquote><br />\n我都唔想接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c42d72aac1be87b473c351e98b66cc799056580","tid":313082,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 還我清純既麻友"},{"pid":"f6886ff739244e1a25a40580ec557391267fcb3f","tid":313082,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我 立即 𨳒你老母啊臭雞<br />\n架純每個毛孔都係c6精液</blockquote><br />\n麻友雞都是"},{"pid":"fc04db82410ec30848700976dff396fb7fee4a29","tid":313082,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fcacecc59fc311d081374fc462d3f0008d0278","tid":313082,"uid":43979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ffd43f5b5f67b1df2660fe9d61281c4b80a467","tid":313082,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"21ed2f8daf9b866d8b953e6db8a5d24ed898abc7","tid":313082,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:03:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲常識嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使乜佢講"},{"pid":"cad6b18848e21f2fccd605a9682b2f224931e81e","tid":313082,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗講都知啦 係班毒撚會幻想處"},{"pid":"3a48bc5b8cd462bd59de909d0434880cb57d0841","tid":313082,"uid":22313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得橘梨紗正過三上幾十倍，三上係靚，但係唔知點解J唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkg